Great basic and easy recipe to put together. I added 1 tablespoon finely minced crystallized ginger and an extra 1/2 teaspoon cinnamon. I used a short 10" coffeecake pan instead of the square pan; I think round tube cakes are easier to serve and are more appetizing. I also added a simple confectioner's maple icing. Great for breakfast.